<keyLead id="201617730C00FFEAFF13FA62FA68FA76" box="[151,1436,1439,1462]" pageId="8" pageNumber="34">
3. Apical band on T1 uninterrupted; labrum slightly curved on apical margin; clypeus flat............. 
